    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several deep scratches, noticeable rust spots on the wheel wells, and faded clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent leak and requires a major tune-up, while the suspension feels quite loose. This is a project car best suited for someone looking for parts or a complete restoration.",
